      "content": "i'm not trying to go to the er at 2am it's just my back. look, i've read online that sometimes doctors suggest higher doses for acute inflammation. if i just took the extra 400mg right now, would that be a huge deal or is it just a precautionary limit? i really need to know if it's safe enough to just do it so i can sleep.",
